{
  "stem": "2966.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So he had a little preferences, and he got some kind of apartment, and they moved out after a short while.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But otherwise, they really had it rough there for the first years.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Next, I went back. '49, I came back here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, we were shipped back by plane from Israel.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was in '49.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I-- we stayed in Paris for about three days, and then we came back to New York.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Came back to New York, the immigration didn't like my papers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They took me to Ellis Island.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I spend there five weeks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They wanted to deport me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But luckily a friend of a friends of a friend knew a judge, and the judge signed some kind of paper, and in one day, they released me.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "After they released me, I went back to working on ships, on American ships.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I worked on ships till almost the end of 1951.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In the meantime, I have met a beautiful girl.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We kept-- I met her sometimes in 1947.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "When I came back from Germany from the DP camp, I brought regards for her from my cousin, from other people, and that's how we met.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Her name, at the time, was Bianca, which is my wife today.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we didn't keep company then, but we saw each other quite often between friends or relatives, her relatives and, and-- but then I started spending more time in New York.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we started going out, which was, I think the first date we had was on her birthday in 1950.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we got engaged, and decided to get married.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We got married on December 1, 1951 in Brooklyn.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was the end of my sailing career.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I never went out after that.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
